  Beastlord -&gt; Tailoring<br>
  Shaman -&gt; Brewing<br>
  Bard -&gt; Pottery<br>
  Rogue -&gt; Baking<br>
  Warrior -&gt; Smithing<br>
<br>
At this point me and 2 friends are doing rogue/warrior/bard quests a 3rd friend will be joining and doing shaman quests.<br>
<br>
Progress on bard quest:<br>
  Citizenship &amp; Initiate Cloak -&gt; Done<br>
  Turn in 3 scorp shells -&gt; Done<br>
  Make clay jar from 4 femurs -&gt; Done<br>
  Collect 4 Young Rockhopper Hides to fashion stretched hide &amp; create drum &amp; shield -&gt; Done<br>
    (At this point the shout from gherik about becoming a bard happens)<br>
  Become errand boy extrodinaire and make a vase -&gt; Done<br>
  Collect 7 owlbear feathers -&gt; Done (loose upgraded cloak here)<br>
  Collect 8 owlbear guts (incomplete no guts seem to drop)<br>
<br>
At this point I have the drum I made and a shield.  If you need any detailed information up to this point feel free to ask, also if you see owlbear guts feel free to say =)<br>
<br>
Warrior Quest completed so far:<br>
  Citizenship &amp; Initiate Cloak -&gt; Done<br>
  &lt;Begin Uncertain Area&gt;<br>
  Turn in 4 femurs -&gt; Done<br>
  Do other stuff<br>
  Make shield frame with smithing<br>
  Do some more stuff<br>
  Turn in sword, frame, cloak and something (global shout about becoming a warrior get everything back) <br>
  &lt;End Uncertain Area&gt;<br>
  Collect Acrylia Flecked Pebbles -&gt; Done<br>
  Collect Rough Ore and smith into bolts -&gt; Done<br>
  Find everything on a shopping list -&gt; Incomplete<br>
     Stuff on list:<br>
        2 Bluetoe Mushrooms (paludal cavern groundspawn)<br>
        1 Bottle of Grinning Grimling (no idea)<br>
        1 Bottle of Rockhopper Red Ale (tavern in shar vahl)<br>
        4 Fatty owlbear meats (owlbear cubs)<br>
<br>
  I can find out the information i'm not clear on later but thats what i can remember off the top of my head.  If anyone has a specific question i can try to answer it, also if anyone knows where to get a bottle of grinning grimling that would be cool too <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
  I'm sure everyone knows how the rogue quests go, friend is on point to look for skulls but hasn't tried yet.<br>
<br>
  Hope this helps.<br>
